{"tid":1220220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上醫院檢控傷者係香港警察好成功嘅一著","createTime":"2019-06-14T03:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:38:26.000Z","uid":175036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae99af3109a470dc0b7604114051de8fef92dff4","tid":1220220,"uid":175036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:16:43.000Z","msg":"固然係方便拉人提升士氣<br />\n重點係可以威嚇參與者<br />\n等佢地唔敢就醫/因要更長時間養傷影響參與後續活動<br />\n冇事/仲考慮緊嘅人更擔心以後受傷/被捕嘅風險<br />\n而就算去醫院嘅人都因為怕被檢控而唔透露受傷經過<br />\n一來壓低武力震壓嘅傷者數字<br />\n二來減少警察被反控告嘅風險<br />\n(一哥面對headshot質詢時意氣風發正正就係依個原因<br />\n「有headshot咩，黎報案啦，告我地就幾年都未上court，你就可以極速入冊休養」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n而咁做佢一句「有罪就你喺邊度都拉」就免卻所有道德責任<br />\n大家話依著狠唔狠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8961cad173da1821540a2a67c8ace3c8bdb680","tid":1220220,"uid":175036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:18:58.000Z","msg":"參考: 醫管局發佈嘅傷者數字<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUp1SFr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUp1SFr.png&h=8d45b723&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"496ea452f81a1325b8829df1b376d235cc906b74","tid":1220220,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"[呼籲]發覺好多黑警del晒自己fb passing out啲相<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1220059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1220059</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f67a5a2fe3db8c7ee6f049ca3aa72495d76de23c","tid":1220220,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:29:22.000Z","msg":"分析得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a80ac4e0b406b689c0b2aed23950ffd3756c70a","tid":1220220,"uid":175036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"參考: 警方就612行動發佈嘅記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z4lEPMTABKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2